# Frontend Environment Variables for Vercel

## Development
- Vite dev proxy automatically routes `/api` to `http://localhost:5000`
- No env file needed

## Production (Vercel)
Create these environment variables in Vercel project settings:

```
VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-url.onrender.com
```

Replace `https://your-backend-url.onrender.com` with your actual Render backend URL (without `/api`).

## Build
```bash
npm run build
```

Vite will automatically inject the env var at build time.
